            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1349315498,
            "creation_date": 1349315498,
            "body": "<p>Use DateTimeFormat.forPattern() with a pattern that does what you want.\nFor instance, <code>DateTimeFormat.forPattern(\"YYYY-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\");<\/code><\/p>\n",
